{"tid":2513284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北韓高官買中國器材　代替歐洲貨　金正恩下令處決","createTime":"2021-05-02T11:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T11:37:03.000Z","uid":261647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c1f69c71a0f1e94be6db06cbd63a84179e43aa","tid":2513284,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/posts/4077618898948292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffans.hkgolden%2Fposts%2F4077618898948292&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtVNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=fe3bce23\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/fans.hkgolden/posts/4077618898948292</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/inO1Ou9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FinO1Ou9.jpg&h=67343ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【北韓高官買中國器材代替歐洲貨 金正恩已下令處決】<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，《每日朝鮮》透露北韓領導人金正恩因為相關官員在為平壤一家醫院購買醫療設備時未有遵從指示，私自購買來自中國的器材，而下令將其處決。<br />\n<br />\n年輕時到德國留學的金正恩，一直對德國先進的醫療設施推崇。在疫情爆發後，他便要求官員盡快興建新醫院，並配備來自德國的設備。由於疫情影響出口，因此這名官員便改向中國，以更優惠的價格購買相同器材。金正恩得悉後大發雷霆，立刻下令將負責進出口的相關官員處死，而另一名被牽涉在內的衛生部高級官員也被解僱。"},{"pid":"da1f9380b5611609a32a575252b472f8d745254a","tid":2513284,"uid":311835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:32:10.000Z","msg":"到底係啲高官貪污 定係真係畀北韓洗腦洗到變弱智 信中國貨係好嘢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddb99d8f8ca5518422ed99e5664d20ab25154727","tid":2513284,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:32:50.000Z","msg":"開箱Kol 我只信金正恩"},{"pid":"9ca30dbd7398fa8e14e9fff2bcfade857a93dc8e","tid":2513284,"uid":225117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:35:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rRWSa1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrRWSa1k.jpg&h=14384e9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"42470209cf1794f4dce4197802d2e8c1f5c967d3","tid":2513284,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:35:49.000Z","msg":"黨鐵呢啲公司大力支持支那國貨"},{"pid":"9639edc57dcd910f154b7d064eb67a7475421ced","tid":2513284,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T11:37:03.000Z","msg":"唔係瑞士留學咩<br />\n屌你老母, 瑞士/德國野變中國野<br />\n係人都嬲啦"}]}